     and asserting faculty; that which obscures or conceals may                
     be judgment, or feeling, but not invention.  The invention,               
     whether good or bad, is in the accurate engineering, not in               
     the fog and uncertainty."                                                 
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
